snippet.title: Ipseity: Arena Playtest Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Ipseity: Arena! Ipseity: Arena is a fast paced arena FPS where you can select different Ipseities, movement types from different games within the Arena FPS franchise that allow for fast paced movement such as bunny hopping, sliding, and walljumping! Engage in foes with quick weapon switch capabilities that allow for fast fragging! Welcome to Ipseity: Arena, and keep on fragging!

Go request access to the playtest below! In order to get access, feel free to join the community discord below and make sure to stay tuned for when more access will be given, as per each update more playtest access will be sent.
GAME:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3149500/Ipseity_Arena/
DISCORD:
https://discord.gg/we42YrTKe6
